Rust ecosystem dependencies
---------------------------

Cave Runtime also depends on the Rust ecosystem crates listed in
Cargo.toml (and resolved transitively in Cargo.lock). All such crates
are independently licensed; the canonical inventory is produced by
`cargo about generate licenses.html` (see CI gate
`.github/workflows/license.yml`).

Pre-1.0 disclaimer
------------------

Cave Runtime is pre-1.0 (target launch: 2026-05-21). License terms,
upstream attribution, and the parity manifest are reviewed every release
cycle; if you redistribute a derived artifact, regenerate this file from
the live `parity.manifest.toml` files at your release point.
